Content: Reporting live from the tallest building in Tokyo. Long ways from them hard ways. Bills and Os and oh-yays. Dade County always, 305 all day. Now, baby, we can parlay or, baby, we can party. She read books, especially about red rooms and tie-ups. I got it hooked, 'cause she seen me in a suit with the red tie tied up. Christian Gris, nice to meet ya, but time is money, only difference is I own it. Now let's stop time and enjoy this moment.
Author: Pitbull
